title: The Office
plot: The Office (versin estadounidense) es una aclamada comedia de falso documental (mockumentary) que retrata el tedioso y divertido da a da de los empleados en la sucursal de Scranton de la empresa papelera Dunder Mifflin. Liderados por el peculiar e incmodo gerente Michael Scott, los trabajadores lidian con bromas, romances y situaciones absurdas de oficina.

episodes.title: Piloto
episodes.description: Una introduccin al personal de la Sucursal de Scranton, Pensilvania de Dunder Mifflin Paper Company.

episodes.title: El da de la diversidad
episodes.description: Despus de que la oficina corporativa descubre que Michael ha estado haciendo comentarios insensibles a sus compaeros de trabajo, envan un Mr. Brown (entrenador de sensibilidad) a la sucursal de Scranton, pero cuando Michael no est de acuerdo con todo lo que dice el entrenador, organiza su propio taller de sensibilidad.

episodes.title: El seguro mdico
episodes.description: Michael transfiere la responsabilidad de elegir un nuevo plan de atencin mdica a Dwight.

episodes.title: El pacto
episodes.description: Jim forma en broma una "alianza" con Dwight cuando surgen rumores de reduccin de personal.

episodes.title: Baloncesto
episodes.description: Es La Oficina vs. El Almacn en un partido de baloncesto.

episodes.title: Chica caliente
episodes.description: Cuando una atractiva vendedora de bolsos llega a la oficina, Michael y Dwight compiten por su atencin.

title: Paquita Salas
plot: Paquita Salas is a peculiar and charismatic talent rep living her most difficult times. She's anchored in the times where fax was king, while trying to adapt to an industry living from Instagram and Whatsapp. On this second season, Paquita will go through many changes in her life that will prove, both to herself and to the rest of the world, how strong and determined she really is. Paquita will understand through a special journey that to be successful in life, the first thing you have to do is to accept yourself. Paquita Salas is an edgy mockumentary full of emotions that will make you cry with laughter.

episodes.title: Casada con esto
episodes.description: Paquita Salas es una de las mejores representantes de actores de Espaa de los 90. Dirige PS Management y cuenta con la actriz Macarena Garca entre sus representantes.

episodes.title: La actriz 360
episodes.description: Paquita regresa de la Seminci de Valladolid. Tras perder a su actriz fetiche, decide liberarse de todo lo que le recuerda a ella y se lanza a cazar talentos.

episodes.title: Hasta Navarrete
episodes.description: La nueva apuesta de la agencia es Mariona Ters. Una llamada inesperada hace que Paquita vuelva a su pueblo, donde se reencuentra con su madre, sus viejos amigos y un antiguo amor.

episodes.title: Divacel
episodes.description: Magi contina enamorada en secreto de lex. Paquita, cansada de no conseguir cstines para Mariona e inspirada en una vendedora ambulante, cambia de tctica.

episodes.title: La Magia que hay en ti
episodes.description: Mariona ha conseguido una pelcula con una promesa del cine espaol. Paquita, como cada ao, invita a la vidente Mara Rosa a que les adivine el futuro.

title: The Sopranos
plot: The Sopranos, writer-producer-director David Chase's extraordinary television series, is nominally an urban gangster drama, but its true impact strikes closer to home: Like 1999's other screen touchstone, American Beauty, the HBO series chronicles a dysfunctional, suburban American family in bold relief. And for protagonist Tony Soprano, there's the added complexity posed by heading twin families, his collegial mob clan and his own, nouveau riche brood.

episodes.title: Pilot
episodes.description: A mobster passes out at a family barbecue and seeks therapy to understand why.

episodes.title: 46 Long
episodes.description: Tony is getting fed up with his mother. Brendan Filone acts against Tony's wishes. Salvatore and Paulie try to track down A.J.'s teacher's stolen car.

episodes.title: Denial, Anger, Acceptance
episodes.description: Tony encourages an unwanted son-in-law to divorce, Carmela learns another secret of Tony's, Meadow experiments with speed to study for the SATs, and Chris and Brendan find out the price of disrespecting Junior.

episodes.title: Meadowlands
episodes.description: Jackie's death leaves a power vacuum, Brendan's death leaves Chris fearing for his life, and Anthony's discovery of what his father really does leaves him confused.

episodes.title: College
episodes.description: While visiting colleges with Meadow, Tony spots a snitch. Carmela, meanwhile, discovers something about Dr. Melfi.

episodes.title: Pax Soprana
episodes.description: Tony tries to balance Junior against the other capos, while Carmela reasserts herself as the woman in Tony's life.

episodes.title: Down Neck
episodes.description: Anthony has disciplinary problems at school, prompting Tony to recount memories of his childhood with Dr. Melfi.

episodes.title: The Legend of Tennessee Moltisanti
episodes.description: The FBI begins closing in on the DiMeo family. Tony and Carmela are angry over all the attention Italians get from the authorities, while Chris fumes that he's not getting enough attention.

episodes.title: Boca
episodes.description: The capos discuss what to do about the local soccer coach, while Junior's mouth causes him some embarrassment.

episodes.title: A Hit is a Hit
episodes.description: Tony tries to branch out into legitimate investments, while Chris and Adriana decide to try their hands at music production.

episodes.title: Nobody Knows Anything
episodes.description: Following the arrest of two of his men, Tony suspects a traitor. Efforts to discover who, however, are stymied.

episodes.title: Isabella
episodes.description: The stress Tony is going through begins to take its toll, and the hit Junior has ordered doesn't help.

episodes.title: I Dream of Jeannie Cusamano
episodes.description: Tony starts cleaning house, while Artie feels torn between keeping the peace in his household, and getting even with Tony for destroying his restaurant.

title: The Crown
plot: The Crown tells the inside story of two of the most famous addresses in the world -- Buckingham Palace and 10 Downing Street - and the intrigues, love lives and machinations behind the great events that shaped the second half of the 20th century. Two houses, two courts, one Crown.

episodes.title: Wolferton Splash
episodes.description: A young Princess Elizabeth marries Prince Philip. As King George VI's health worsens, Winston Churchill is elected prime minister for the second time.

episodes.title: Hyde Park Corner
episodes.description: With King George too ill to travel, Elizabeth and Philip embark on a four-continent Commonwealth tour. Party leaders attempt to undermine Churchill.

episodes.title: Windsor
episodes.description: With Elizabeth in new role, Philip tries to assert some power. Churchill wants to delay the coronation. King George's disgraced brother arrives.

episodes.title: Act of God
episodes.description: When dense smog cripples London for days and creates a serious health hazard, Churchill's inaction leaves him vulnerable to his political enemies.

episodes.title: Smoke and Mirrors
episodes.description: Elizabeth rejects protocol by appointing Philip to coordinate her coronation, but his ideas create conflict. The Duke of Windsor returns to London.

episodes.title: Gelignite
episodes.description: Margaret and Peter come to Elizabeth with a request. With a royal scandal about to break in the newspapers, the Queen Mother intervenes.

episodes.title: Scientia Potentia Est
episodes.description: As the Soviets test the H-bomb, both Churchill and Eden have major health crises. Angry about her inadequate education, Elizabeth hires a tutor.

episodes.title: Pride and Joy
episodes.description: Elizabeth and Philip go on an exhausting world journey. Margaret takes over some of her sister's official duties and tries to liven things up.

episodes.title: Assassins
episodes.description: As tensions with Philip increase, Elizabeth spends time with her old friend Porchey. Churchill's portrait is painted for his 80th birthday.

episodes.title: Gloriana
episodes.description: Margaret and Peter are reunited, but another obstacle stands in their way. Elizabeth is torn between her duty as Queen and her love for her sister.
